*rubyripper-0.4.1 (12 May 2007)

  12 May 2007; Steve Dibb <beandog@gentoo.org> +rubyripper-0.4.1.ebuild:
  version bump, bug 176836

  03 Feb 2007; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.3.ebuild:
  stable on amd64; bug 155701

  03 Feb 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.3.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug 155701

  05 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> -rubyripper-0.2.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

  05 Dec 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.3.ebuild:
  Remove an unneeded sed, thanks to Bouke Woudstra (upstream) for reporting.
  Use elog instead of einfo.

  04 Dec 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rubyripper-0.3.ebuild:
  Remove cdrtools dependency, cdda2wav is no more supported.

